result.name: 阿堂魚湯

reviews.text:
fish soup based with undo. you can feel free to add topping for your noodles. 

many choices, can serve with undo or rice. serve quick after order. per head around hkd 80. 

the soup is full of fish flavour, almost bottom up the undo soup. 

they serve sake and palm wine as well. I was there around 8pm on Friday, quite a lot of people.

the oyster undo is good. oyster is crispy and quite big. 

would be a choice if you prefer a full but light meal
No. See you never, not dining with roachies again
A small shop located on Lai Chi Kok Road which is easy to get access by MTR. The food is really good and price is very attractive. Fish soup base noodle, udon or ramen are signature dishes.
Oyster fish soup hot pot is wonderful. The soup is light taste since it is low salt and oyster is yummy.
Good deal at lunch time.

result.name: 阿堂魚湯

reviews.text: 性價比高的餐廳，大力推薦鹽燒三文魚頭魚鮫及炸軟殼蟹沙律

聽個名以為係湯飯之類，原來係曰本菜，試咗個吉列炸豬扒午餐，件扒都幾大件，食落唔太油，Ok.
地方唔算太大，尚算舒服. 服務都ok
這個飽魚花膠魚肚湯飯幾好，但魚湯淡左啲，可以自己喜好加味。

餐廳環境麻麻，一入餐廳就有朕垃圾及霉味。
所謂招牌菜魚湯淡而無味，只有咸同腥味。配搭其他配料均沒有味道。
不推薦。
鹽燒三文魚頭鮫
